Monday morning follow ups 👩🏻‍💻

Sold! 🤩
Stunning almost 8,000 sq ft home sitting on 9.5 acres with a stocked lake, walking trail, tennis courts, pool & 5 car garage. 
Originally listed at $1.9 million, my clients were able to snag it for $500k under asking price after several days of negotiating with a quick cash close! This property belonged to Mickey Gilley and his family poured so much love into it for the last few decades. From the custom chandeliers, the recording studio, built in refrigerator and fully tiled pool… this home was left with no stone unturned. 
One of a kind property & I am so thankful to have represented my clients at the best of my ability for this one. 🍾🎊

Feeling so thankful for how busy I’ve been these last couple months! 
Currently working on several listings and multiple sellers/buyers under contract. 🙏🏼 

I know a lot of you are waiting on the market to crash, but there is no crash in the foreseeable future. Although, interest rates have been fluctuating, inventory is still low. This being said, housing prices are expected to stay high and continue to increase. Refinancing is always an option but paying present prices in the future is not. 

If you’ve been on the fence in regards to purchasing or selling your home, shoot me a message, and I would be more than happy to discuss what your options are 👋🏼😊
